 spontaneous polarization.\nThe tunable bandgaps in general and possible indirect-direct bandgap\ntransitions due to tensile strain or external electric field endow the TMD\nheterobilayer materials a viable candidate for optoelectronic applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Dec 2013 20:17:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-05"}
